# shadcn/ui

- Build all UI with [shadcn/ui](https://ui.shadcn.com/) primitives and patterns. Prefer importing from the project’s shadcn components (e.g. `components/ui/*`) over ad-hoc styled HTML for buttons, dialogs, forms, etc.

## Project not set up yet

If there is no shadcn setup (no `components.json` / shadcn config), initialize from the repo root:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest init
```

## Missing component

If a component from the registry is not installed, add it by name from the repo root (example: `button`):

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add button
```

Replace `button` with the component you need (`dialog`, `input`, `dropdown-menu`, etc.).
